ftbuniversity.etechchap.title=Environmental Tech

ftbuniversity.digitalguide.subtitle=Get the Digital Guide
ftbuniversity.digitalguide.desc=The &bDigital Guide&r is your one-stop shop for all mods by ValkyrieofNight. We only have &eEnvironmental Tech&r, so that's all that's in the Guide.

ftbuniversity.etassembler.subtitle=制作一个 Assembler
ftbuniversity.etassembler.desc1=All Environmental Tech machines are multiblocks, built around their Controllers.
ftbuniversity.etassembler.desc2=The &bAssembler&r will automatically build the multiblock when used on the multiblock's Controller, given that you have the blocks required.

ftbuniversity.voidore1.title=RF to Ores
ftbuniversity.voidore1.subtitle=制作一个 Void Ore Miner Controller Tier 1
ftbuniversity.voidore1.desc1=&bVoid Ore Miners&r are generally the biggest point of interest in the mod. They use RF to slowly &6generate ores&r. Higher tiers work faster, use more power, and choose from a larger pool to generate.
ftbuniversity.voidore1.desc2=&bTier 1&r uses &6660RF/t&r and generates an ore every &6400 ticks&r. It &6takes up a 7x4x7 area&r.
ftbuniversity.voidore1.desc3=For all Void Ore Miners, the &6Laser Core must have a direct line of sight to Bedrock or the void under&r.
ftbuniversity.voidore1.desc4=The &6Laser Lens' color can influence the weight of certain ores&r, making them more likely to generate.

ftbuniversity.etechreadguide=See the Digital Guide for the block requirements.

ftbuniversity.voidore2.title=Yep, You Have to Make &lEvery Single One&r
ftbuniversity.voidore2.subtitle=制作一个 Void Ore Miner Controller Tier 2
ftbuniversity.voidore2.desc=&bTier 2&r uses &6575RF/t&r and generates an ore every &6320 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up a 7x5x7 area&r.

ftbuniversity.etechmodifiers=You can &6replace the Null Modifiers with other Modifiers to upgrade&r the multiblock.

ftbuniversity.voidore3.subtitle=制作一个 Void Ore Miner Controller Tier 3
ftbuniversity.voidore3.desc=&bTier 3&r uses &6750RF/t&r and generates an ore every &6160 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up an 11x6x11 area&r.

ftbuniversity.voidore4.subtitle=制作一个 Void Ore Miner Controller Tier 4
ftbuniversity.voidore4.desc=&bTier 4&r uses &6900RF/t&r and generates an ore every &680 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up an 11x7x11 area&r.

ftbuniversity.voidore5.subtitle=制作一个 Void Ore Miner Controller Tier 5
ftbuniversity.voidore5.desc=&bTier 5&r uses &61,000RF/t&r and generates an ore every &640 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up an 11x8x11 area&r.

ftbuniversity.voidore6.subtitle=制作一个 Void Ore Miner Controller Tier 6
ftbuniversity.voidore6.desc=&bTier 6&r uses &6800RF/t&r and generates an ore every &620 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up a 13x8x13 area&r.

ftbuniversity.voidres1.title=RF to Non-Ore Blocks
ftbuniversity.voidres1.subtitle=制作一个 Void Resource Miner Controller Tier 1
ftbuniversity.voidres1.desc1=&bVoid Resource Miners&r will &6generate Stone, Dirt, Grass, and the like&r using RF. Higher tiers do not get new resources, they only work faster.
ftbuniversity.voidres1.desc2=&bTier 1&r uses &6160RF/t&r and generates a resource every &6400 ticks&r. It &6takes up a 7x4x7 area&r.

ftbuniversity.voidres2.subtitle=制作一个 Void Resource Miner Controller Tier 2
ftbuniversity.voidres2.desc=&bTier 2&r uses &6100RF/t&r and generates a resource every &6320 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up a 7x5x7 area&r.

ftbuniversity.voidres3.subtitle=制作一个 Void Resource Miner Controller Tier 3
ftbuniversity.voidres3.desc=&bTier 3&r uses &6100RF/t&r and generates a resource every &6160 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up an 11x6x11 area&r.

ftbuniversity.voidres4.subtitle=制作一个 Void Resource Miner Controller Tier 4
ftbuniversity.voidres4.desc=&bTier 3&r uses &6100RF/t&r and generates a resource every &680 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up an 11x7x11 area&r.

