ftbuniversity.voidres5.desc=&bTier 3&r uses &6100RF/t&r and generates a resource every &640 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up an 11x8x11 area&r.

ftbuniversity.voidres6.subtitle=制作一个 Void Resource Miner Controller Tier 6
ftbuniversity.voidres6.desc=&bTier 3&r uses &6100RF/t&r and generates a resource every &620 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up a 13x8x13 area&r.

ftbuniversity.voidbot1.title=RF to Plants
ftbuniversity.voidbot1.subtitle=制作一个 Void Botanic Miner Tier 1
ftbuniversity.voidbot1.desc1=&bVoid Botanic Miners&r will &6generate all plant matter (wood, saplings, flowers, etc)&r using RF. This includes plants from other mods, like Forestry and Botania! Higher tiers do not get new resources, they only work faster.
ftbuniversity.voidbot1.desc2=&bTier 1&r uses &6160RF/t&r and generates a plant every &6400 ticks&r. It &6takes up a 7x4x7 area&r.

ftbuniversity.voidbot2.subtitle=制作一个 Void Botanic Miner Controller Tier 2
ftbuniversity.voidbot2.desc=&bTier 2&r uses &6100RF/t&r and generates a plant every &6320 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up a 7x5x7 area&r.

ftbuniversity.voidbot3.subtitle=制作一个 Void Botanic Miner Controller Tier 3
ftbuniversity.voidbot3.desc=&bTier 3&r uses &6100RF/t&r and generates a plant every &6160 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up an 11x6x11 area&r.

ftbuniversity.voidbot4.subtitle=制作一个 Void Botanic Miner Controller Tier 4
ftbuniversity.voidbot4.desc=&bTier 4&r uses &6100RF/t&r and generates a plant every &680 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up an 11x7x11 area&r.

ftbuniversity.voidbot5.subtitle=制作一个 Void Botanic Miner Controller Tier 5
ftbuniversity.voidbot5.desc=&bTier 5&r uses &6100RF/t&r and generates a plant every &640 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up an 11x8x11 area&r.

ftbuniversity.voidbot6.subtitle=制作一个 Void Botanic Miner Controller Tier 6
ftbuniversity.voidbot6.desc=&bTier 6&r uses &6100RF/t&r and generates a plant every &620 ticks&r without upgrades. It &6takes up a 13x8x13 area&r.

ftbuniversity.etlight1.title=Lightning to RF
ftbuniversity.etlight1.subtitle=制作一个 Lightning Controller Tier 1
ftbuniversity.etlight1.desc1=&bLightning Rods&r  &6generate a massive amount of RF&r when struck by lightning. It does not make RF when struck by lightning caused by other mods.
ftbuniversity.etlight1.desc2=Every 1,600-3,200 ticks, it has a chance to get struck by lightning. During a thunderstorm, it changes to once every 400-800 ticks.
ftbuniversity.etlight1.desc3=&6Higher tiers have a &n&llower&r&6 chance of being hit, but generate more RF.&r
ftbuniversity.etlight1.desc4=&bTier 1&r has a &660%% chance&r of being struck, and &6generates 93,750-750,000RF&r.

ftbuniversity.etlight2.subtitle=制作一个 Lightning Controller Tier 2
ftbuniversity.etlight2.desc=&bTier 2&r has a &655%% chance&r of being struck, and &6generates 281,500-2,250,000RF&r.

ftbuniversity.etlight3.subtitle=制作一个 Lightning Controller Tier 3
ftbuniversity.etlight3.desc=&bTier 3&r has a &650%% chance&r of being struck, and &6generates 1,312,500-10,500,000RF&r.

ftbuniversity.etlight4.subtitle=制作一个 Lightning Controller Tier 4
ftbuniversity.etlight4.desc=&bTier 4&r has a &645%% chance&r of being struck, and &6generates 5,062,500-40,500,000RF&r.

ftbuniversity.etlight5.subtitle=制作一个 Lightning Controller Tier 5
ftbuniversity.etlight5.desc=&bTier 5&r has a &640%% chance&r of being struck, and &6generates 19,500,000-156,000,000RF&r.

ftbuniversity.etlight6.subtitle=制作一个 Lightning Controller Tier 6
ftbuniversity.etlight6.desc=&bTier 6&r has a &635%% chance&r of being struck, and &6generates 74,250,000-594,000,000RF&r.

ftbuniversity.etsolar1.title=Time to RF
ftbuniversity.etsolar1.subtitle=制作一个 Solar Array Controller Tier 1
ftbuniversity.etsolar1.desc1=&bSolar Arrays&r &6generate a fairly high amount of RF/t when it can see the sun&r. They work worse during storms.
ftbuniversity.etsolar1.desc2=Like there are 6 tiers of Controllers, there are &66 tiers of Solar Cells&r. Solar Cells of any tier can be used with any Controller, with &6higher tiers making more RF/t&r.
ftbuniversity.etsolar1.desc3=These quests will assume you're using the same tier for both.
ftbuniversity.etsolar1.desc4=&bTier 1&r will generate &6549RF/t&r.

ftbuniversity.etsolar2.subtitle=制作一个 Solar Array Controller Tier 2
ftbuniversity.etsolar2.desc=&bTier 2&r will generate &64,075RF/t&r.

ftbuniversity.etsolar3.subtitle=制作一个 Solar Array Controller Tier 3
ftbuniversity.etsolar3.desc=&bTier 3&r will generate &624,059RF/t&r.

ftbuniversity.etsolar4.subtitle=制作一个 Solar Array Controller Tier 4
ftbuniversity.etsolar4.desc=&bTier 4&r will generate &6106,110RF/t&r.

ftbuniversity.etsolar5.subtitle=制作一个 Solar Array Controller Tier 5
ftbuniversity.etsolar5.desc=&bTier 5&r will generate &6475,772RF/t&r.

ftbuniversity.etsolar6.subtitle=制作一个 Solar Array Controller Tier 6
ftbuniversity.etsolar6.desc=&bTier 6&r will generate &61,771,965RF/t&r.

ftbuniversity.etranged1.title=RF Beacon
ftbuniversity.etranged1.subtitle=制作一个 Ranged Nano Bot Beacon Tier 1
ftbuniversity.etranged1.desc1=&bRanged Nano Bot Beacons&r will &6give players within their range effects chosen by Modifiers&r.
ftbuniversity.etranged1.desc2=The Modifiers all &6share a name with the effect&r they would give you (Resistance gives you Resistance, etc). The Digital Guide shows which Modifiers can be installed to it.
ftbuniversity.etranged1.desc3=The RF cost is entirely dependant on the Modifiers.
ftbuniversity.etranged1.desc4=Higher tiers have &6higher range&r and can have &6more Modifiers&r.
ftbuniversity.etranged1.desc5=&bTier 1&r has a range of &632 blocks&r and room for &64 Modifiers&r.

ftbuniversity.etranged2.subtitle=制作一个 Ranged Nano Bot Beacon Tier 2
ftbuniversity.etranged2.desc=&bTier 2&r has a range of &648 blocks&r and room for &68 Modifiers&r.

ftbuniversity.etranged3.subtitle=制作一个 Ranged Nano Bot Beacon Tier 3
ftbuniversity.etranged3.desc=&bTier 3&r has a range of &664 blocks&r and room for &612 Modifiers&r.

ftbuniversity.etranged4.subtitle=制作一个 Ranged Nano Bot Beacon Tier 4
ftbuniversity.etranged4.desc=&bTier 4&r has a range of &680 blocks&r and room for &616 Modifiers&r.

ftbuniversity.etranged5.subtitle=制作一个 Ranged Nano Bot Beacon Tier 5
ftbuniversity.etranged5.desc=&bTier 5&r has a range of &696 blocks&r and room for &620 Modifiers&r.

ftbuniversity.etranged6.subtitle=制作一个 Ranged Nano Bot Beacon Tier 6
ftbuniversity.etranged6.desc=&bTier 6&r has a range of &6112 blocks&r and room for &624 Modifiers&r.

ftbuniversity.etpersonal1.title=Player Upgrades
ftbuniversity.etpersonal1.subtitle=制作一个 Personal Nano Bot Beacon Tier 1
ftbuniversity.etpersonal1.desc1=&bPersonal Nano Bot Beacons&r will &6give their owner effects chosen by Modifiers with infinite range&r.
ftbuniversity.etpersonal1.desc2=There are Modifiers for &6every potion effect&r, as well as &6creative-style flight&r and &6flight-speed&r. The Digital Guide shows which Modifiers can be installed to it.
ftbuniversity.etpersonal1.desc3=The RF cost is entirely dependant on the Modifiers, though it takes 512 more RF/t than the Ranged equivalent.
ftbuniversity.etpersonal1.desc4=&bTier 1&r has room for &64 Modifiers&r.

ftbuniversity.etpersonal2.subtitle=制作一个 Personal Nano Bot Beacon Tier 2
ftbuniversity.etpersonal2.desc=&bTier 2&r has room for &68 Modifiers&r.

ftbuniversity.etpersonal3.subtitle=制作一个 Personal Nano Bot Beacon Tier 3
ftbuniversity.etpersonal3.desc=&bTier 3&r has room for &612 Modifiers&r.

ftbuniversity.etpersonal4.subtitle=制作一个 Personal Nano Bot Beacon Tier 4
ftbuniversity.etpersonal4.desc=&bTier 4&r has room for &616 Modifiers&r.

ftbuniversity.etpersonal5.subtitle=制作一个 Personal Nano Bot Beacon Tier 5
ftbuniversity.etpersonal5.desc=&bTier 5&r has room for &620 Modifiers&r.

ftbuniversity.etpersonal6.subtitle=制作一个 Personal Nano Bot Beacon Tier 6
ftbuniversity.etpersonal6.desc=&bTier 6&r has room for &624 Modifiers&r.

ftbuniversity.etmodifiers.title=Upgrades
ftbuniversity.etmodifiers.subtitle=Make Modifiers
ftbuniversity.etmodifiers.desc1=Most ETech multiblocks use Null Modifiers somewhere in the structure.
ftbuniversity.etmodifiers.desc2=You can &6replace these Null Modifiers&r with other &bModifiers&r, depending on the machine, and their effects will be applied.
ftbuniversity.etmodifiers.desc3=There's normally no in-game explanation for what they do, so &6we've manually added tooltips&r to them.
