ftbuniversity.celestnotes.title=That's Rough, Buddy
ftbuniversity.celestnotes.subtitle=Get Celestial Notes
ftbuniversity.celestnotes.desc1=Sometimes when theorycrafting, a research card might ask for &bCelestial Notes&r.
ftbuniversity.celestnotes.desc2=To get Celestial Notes, &6use the Thaumometer to scan the sky&r while you have Paper and Scribing Tools.
ftbuniversity.celestnotes.desc3=It should be fairly obvious how you get each type. Scan the sun to get "Solar", scan the northern night sky to get "Stellar, Northern Quadrant", etc.
ftbuniversity.celestnotes.desc4=You can only scan each &6once per night&r.
ftbuniversity.celestnotes.task=Celestial Notes
ftbuniversity.celestnotes.rewards=Celestial Notes

ftbuniversity.thaumometer.subtitle=制作一个 Thaumometer
ftbuniversity.thaumometer.desc1=The &bThaumometer&r allows you to scan things, learning their aspects and &6making progress in Observations&r. Everything can only be scanned once.
ftbuniversity.thaumometer.desc2=&6Scanning an inventory&r will also scan its contents.
ftbuniversity.thaumometer.desc3=While holding the Thaumometer, the top left will show a gauge showing &6the chunk's Vis and Flux&r.

ftbuniversity.thaumalchemy.title=Understanding, Deconstructing, and Reconstructing
ftbuniversity.thaumalchemy.subtitle=Unlock Alchemy
ftbuniversity.thaumalchemy.desc1=&bAlchemy&r is the first school of magic unlocked. It has to do with &6deconstructing items into their base aspects&r, and then using it.
ftbuniversity.thaumalchemy.desc2=Use Salis Mundus on a Cauldron to 制作一个 &bCrucible&r. Place a &6heat source&r below (fire, lava, etc) and fill it with &6water&r until it boils.
ftbuniversity.thaumalchemy.desc3=&6Throwing an item into the boiling water&r will instantly destroy it, filling the Crucible with that item's Essentia.
ftbuniversity.thaumalchemy.desc4=Certain items, if thrown in, will use Essentia that's already in the Crucible to &6craft a new item instead&r.
ftbuniversity.thaumalchemy.desc5=If Essentia is left too long in the Crucible, it will dissipate into the atmosphere, &6converting to Flux&r. You can throw &6Quartz Slivers&r in, and it will bind to whatever Essentia is there to &6create Vis Crystals&r of that aspect.
ftbuniversity.thaumalchemy.desc6=A good recipe for Nitor is 2 Torch + 1 Coal, then Glowstone as the catalyst. This leaves 1 Crystal's worth of Bestia.

ftbuniversity.alumentum.title=Alumentum, Gentille Alumentum 
ftbuniversity.alumentum.subtitle=制作一个lumentum
ftbuniversity.alumentum.desc1=&bAlumentum&r can be thrown, causing an explosion. It also works as furnace fuel, and &6fuel for the Essentia Smeltery&r.
ftbuniversity.alumentum.desc2=When used in the Essentia Smeltery, it &6increases the speed by 20%%&r.
ftbuniversity.alumentum.desc3=A good recipe for Alumentum is 2 Coal + 2 Redstone + 2 Gunpowder, then 4 Coal as the catalyst. This leaves 2.5 Crystal's worth of Alkimia. Doubling this will remove the risk of Flux.
ftbuniversity.alumentum.desc4=Remember: &cyou cannot craft Alumentum until it is unlocked in the Thaumonomicon&r. This is true for everything.

ftbuniversity.alchemicmetal.title=Magic Metal
ftbuniversity.alchemicmetal.subtitle=制作一个lchemical Brass and Thaumium
ftbuniversity.alchemicmetal.desc1=&bAlchemic Brass&r is a rather simple alloy; however, it &6combines metal and magic&r rather two different metals.
ftbuniversity.alchemicmetal.desc2=A good recipe for it would be 2 Flint, then 2 Iron Ingots for the catalyst. This leaves behind 5 Crystal's worth of Terra.
ftbuniversity.alchemicmetal.desc3=&bThaumium&r is slightly more advanced, and much more magically capable. It can be made into tools and armor, which are comparable to Iron but are &6incredibly enchantable&r.
ftbuniversity.alchemicmetal.desc4=A good, early recipe for Thaumium would be 1 Flint + 1 Salis Mundus, then an Iron Ingot as the catalyst. This leaves 2.5 Crystal's worth of Terra and Potentia.
ftbuniversity.alchemicmetal.desc5=Later on, you can farm Nether Wart for Vitium, then centrifuge it into Praecantatio.
ftbuniversity.alchemicmetal.rewards=Magic Alloys

ftbuniversity.essentiasmelting1.title=Purple Goop
ftbuniversity.essentiasmelting1.subtitle=制作一个 Essentia Smeltery
ftbuniversity.essentiasmelting1.desc1=The &bEssentia Smelter&r will &6break items down into unprocessed Essentia&r, converting about 20%% into Flux.
ftbuniversity.essentiasmelting1.desc2=Slowly, this Essentia Slurry is split into &bArcane Alembics&r placed atop the Smelter. You can stack up to 5 Alembics on the Smelter, allowing up to 5 Aspects to be split from the Slurry.
ftbuniversity.essentiasmelting1.desc3=Essentia can be removed from the Slurry by clicking &6Phials&r (or &6Warded Jars&r, if you're sneaking) on them.

ftbuniversity.essentiasmelting2.title=Purble Place
ftbuniversity.essentiasmelting2.subtitle=制作一个 Thaumium Essentia Smelter
ftbuniversity.essentiasmelting2.desc1=The &bThaumium Essentia Smelter&r works at &690%% efficiency&r, rather than the first tier's 80%%.
ftbuniversity.essentiasmelting2.desc2=It also breaks down Slurry &6twice as fast&r.

ftbuniversity.essentiasmelting3.title=The Good Stuff
ftbuniversity.essentiasmelting3.subtitle=制作一个 Void Metal Essentia Smelter
ftbuniversity.essentiasmelting3.desc=The &bVoid Metal Essentia Smelter&r works at &695%% efficiency&r, but is slower than the Thaumium Smelter.

ftbuniversity.wardedjar.subtitle=制作一个 Warded Jar
ftbuniversity.wardedjar.desc1=&bWarded Jars&r can store up to &6250 Essentia&r of a single type.
ftbuniversity.wardedjar.desc2=You can attach a &6Jar Label&r, and it will display what Aspect it stores. If it empties after a Label is set, it will stay set, allowing only that Aspect to enter.
ftbuniversity.wardedjar.desc3=Sneak clicking a Jar with an empty hand will clear it out.

ftbuniversity.voidjar.subtitle=制作一个 Void Jar
ftbuniversity.voidjar.desc=The &bVoid Jar&r works exactly like the Warded Jar, but it accepts Essentia even when full. This extra Essentia will be lost, but not dissipate into Flux.

ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.title=Use These for Like, Ten Minutes
ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.subtitle=Make Essentia Tubes
ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.desc1=&bEssentia Tubes&r allow you to automatically &6transfer Essentia&r, generally from Alembics to Jars. They're surprisingly complex, not at all like pipes from other mods.
ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.desc2=When attached to a Jar, it will create &6suction&r, which will attempt to pull Essentia. You can tell the suction by using an &bEssentia Resonator&r on the Jar. Suction &6decreases with distance&r.
ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.desc3=Using the Resonator on a Tube will show what Aspect is being sucked, and the sucking power. You can use this to find what's gumming up the Tubes, so you can fix or disconnect it.
ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.desc4=You can break connections by sneak right-clicking the Caster's Gauntlet on them.
ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.desc5=&6Multiple types of Essentia can not flow through the same tube.&r
ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.desc6=There are several types of Tube:
ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.desc7=• &bEssentia Tube&r: plain old Tubes
ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.desc8=• &bEssentia Valve&r: can be toggled (with click or redstone), stopping suction and flow through it
ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.desc9=• &bRestricted Essentia Tube&r: halves the power of suction that passes through
ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.desc10=• &bDirectional Essentia Tube&r: suction can only be provided from the blue end
ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.desc11=• &bFiltered Essentia Tube&r: only allows a specific Aspect to be sucked through; set with a Phial
ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.desc12=• &bEssentia Buffer&r: stores less than normal, but can have up to 8 Aspects flowing through at the same time. Can block sucking to only one side (blue=allowed, red=disallowed)
ftbuniversity.essentiatubes.task=Essentia Tubes

# Taken from https://minecraftguides.net/tc6/alchemy/essentia-tubes
ftbuniversity.optimaltube.title=Totally Tubular
ftbuniversity.optimaltube.subtitle=Learn the optimal way to store Essentia with Tubes
ftbuniversity.optimaltube.desc1=For &boptimal Alembic→Jar storage&r, run Essentia Tubes &6from the Alembic to a Buffer&r, and attach a Bellows.
ftbuniversity.optimaltube.desc2=Place &619 Buffers&r after it, with a &6Filtered Tube on each side&r (making a 3 wide. 19 long line). That's &638 Filtered Tubes&r, for &637 Aspects&r.
ftbuniversity.optimaltube.desc3=Use the Caster's Gauntlet to &6disconnect each Filtered Tube from each other&r, so they're only attached to the Buffers. Sneak click the back-end of each Buffer, setting them red, so they &6only pull from Buffers in front of them&r.
ftbuniversity.optimaltube.desc4=&6Set&r each Filtered Tube to an Aspect, then place a &6Warded Jar underneath&r.
ftbuniversity.optimaltube.desc5=Place a &6Restricted Tube&r at the end of each Filtered Tube (disconnect them from each other), and place a &6Void Jar under each&r.
ftbuniversity.optimaltube.desc6=This setup should be able to handle as much Essentia as you can throw at it (though only from one Alembic). It will store up to 500 Essentia of each type, and then void the excess.

ftbuniversity.auxslurry.subtitle=制作一个 Auxiliary Slurry Pump
ftbuniversity.auxslurry.desc1=The &bAuxiliary Slurry Pump&r can be placed on the side of an Essentia Smelter, and it will make it &6faster and more efficient&r.
ftbuniversity.auxslurry.desc2=It will output refined Essentia to Alembics above itself.

ftbuniversity.auxvent.subtitle=制作一个 Auxiliary Venting Port
ftbuniversity.auxvent.desc=The &bAuxiliary Venting Port&r can be placed on the sides of an Essentia Smelter to &6decrease the amount of Flux&r it creates.

ftbuniversity.essentiacentrifuge.title=Essence of SPEEEN
ftbuniversity.essentiacentrifuge.subtitle=制作一个 Essentia Centrifuge
ftbuniversity.essentiacentrifuge.desc1=The &bEssentia Centrifuge&r will &6separate compount Essentia into its components&r.
ftbuniversity.essentiacentrifuge.desc2=This is beyond useful if certain Aspects (like Praecantatio) are hard to get, but they form a part of an Aspect that's easily farmable (like Vitium from Nether Wart).
ftbuniversity.essentiacentrifuge.desc3=The input Essentia must &6enter the bottom&r, and the resultant Essentia &6exits the top&r.

ftbuniversity.thaumatorium.title=Thaumatorium
ftbuniversity.thaumatorium.subtitle=制作一个 Thaumatorium
ftbuniversity.thaumatorium.desc1=The &bThaumatorium&r is a multiblock that can &6automatically craft alchemic recipes&r.
ftbuniversity.thaumatorium.desc2=Place the catalyst item in the top left, then choose which item you want to make.
ftbuniversity.thaumatorium.desc3=Provide the correct Essentia from any side of the 2 top blocks, and items will be &6ejected from the front center face&r.
ftbuniversity.thaumatorium.desc4=A &6Mnemonic Matrix&r placed on the side will allow it to handle 2 additional recipes. You can install multiple.
ftbuniversity.thaumatorium.task=Look at a Thaumatorium

ftbuniversity.wirelessessentia.title=Wireless Essentia
ftbuniversity.wirelessessentia.subtitle=制作一个 Filling and Emptying Essentia Transfuser
ftbuniversity.wirelessessentia.desc1=The &bFilling Essentia Transfuser&r can be placed on a source of Essentia (like an Alembic), and it will send the Essentia through the air to any Jar within 16 blocks that it can see.
ftbuniversity.wirelessessentia.desc2=The &bEmptying Essentia Transfuser&r does the opposite, placed on a destination (like the Thaumatorium), and it will try to fill it from Jars within 16 blocks.
ftbuniversity.wirelessessentia.desc3=Used with &6Essentia Mirrors&r, this can make the Thaumatorium absurdly simple to use. Simply place one Mirror in the &6storage room&r, and another &6next to the Thaumatorium&r with an Emptying Transfuser on it, and it will try to &6pull through the Mirror&r.

ftbuniversity.tallow.title=Alchemical Duplication
ftbuniversity.tallow.subtitle=Complete Hedge Alchemy
ftbuniversity.tallow.desc1=&bHedge Alchemy&r is one of the first branches of alchemy you can unlock.
ftbuniversity.tallow.desc2=It unlocks &bMagic Tallow&r, which is kinda gross but sorta useful, but the research also allows you to duplicate certain items!

ftbuniversity.everful.subtitle=制作一个 Everful Urn
ftbuniversity.everful.desc1=The &bEverful Urn&r will slowly &6fill up any nearby fluid containers&r with Water.
ftbuniversity.everful.desc2=This is most useful for the Crucible, but also works on the Petal Apothecary!
ftbuniversity.everful.desc3=You can also pipe Water out the top, and it never runs out.

ftbuniversity.liquiddeath.title=Just Like Mom Used To Make
ftbuniversity.liquiddeath.subtitle=制作一个 Liquid Death Bucket
ftbuniversity.liquiddeath.desc1=&bLiquid Death&r will deal 2 hearts of damage per second to anything that's standing in it.
ftbuniversity.liquiddeath.desc2=Mobs killed will also &6drop Vis Crystals&r.

ftbuniversity.bathsalt.title=Now With 60%% Less Foaming At the Mouth
ftbuniversity.bathsalt.subtitle=Make Purifying Bath Salts
ftbuniversity.bathsalt.desc=Throwing &bPurifying Bath Salts&r into Water then jumping in will give you some &6relief from Warp&r.

ftbuniversity.arcanespa.title=Gamer Bath Water
ftbuniversity.arcanespa.subtitle=制作一个 Arcane Spa
ftbuniversity.arcanespa.desc=The &bArcane Spa&r can be filled with Water and Purifying Bath Salts, and it will pour the Purifying Fluid into the world in a 5x5 area above it.

ftbuniversity.sansoap.subtitle=Make Sanity Soap
ftbuniversity.sansoap.desc=&bSanity Soap&r can be used to &6remove all temporary warp&r, and has a &6chance to lower permanent warp&r.

ftbuniversity.auramancy.title=No Foolish Wand Waving
ftbuniversity.auramancy.subtitle=Unlock Auramancy
ftbuniversity.auramancy.desc1=&bAuramancy&r is the second school of magic, and it deals with the creation and casting of &6spells&r.
ftbuniversity.auramancy.desc2=The main thing you need from it is the &bCaster's Gauntlet&r. Though, with no spells, it only serves as a magical wrench.

ftbuniversity.focalmanip.title=Spellcrafting
ftbuniversity.focalmanip.subtitle=制作一个 Focal Manipulator
ftbuniversity.focalmanip.desc1=In Thaumcraft 6, &6spells are custom-created&r by you. This is done in the &bFocal Manipulator&r.
ftbuniversity.focalmanip.desc2=Insert a &bBlank Lesser Focus&r (higher tiers can be more powerful/complex), choose a &6medium&r (how the spell is transferred), then choose an &6effect&r (what the spell does).
ftbuniversity.focalmanip.desc3=On the right, you can see its &6complexity&r, how many levels of &6experience&r it costs to make, and how much &6Vis&r it costs to create and cast, and then what &6Vis Crystals&r you need to craft it.
ftbuniversity.focalmanip.desc4=You can also click on certain components (usually effects) to &6change certain elements&r of it, increasing its complexity.
ftbuniversity.focalmanip.desc5=Give it a name, get the required Crystals, and then click the button at the top right to &6craft&r it.
ftbuniversity.focalmanip.desc6=Once you have your Spell Focus, hold your Caster's Gauntlet and hold the &6Change Focus Cast&r button (see controls). Hover over the Focus you want, then let go of the button to equip it. Press the button &6while sneaking&r to remove the Focus entirely.

ftbuniversity.thaumfocus2.subtitle=制作一个 Blank Advanced Focus
ftbuniversity.thaumfocus2.desc=The &bAdvanced Focus&r has a maximum of &625&r complexity, compared to the Lesser's &615&r.

ftbuniversity.thaumfocus3.subtitle=制作一个 Blank Greater Focus
ftbuniversity.thaumfocus3.desc=The &bGreater Focus&r has a maximum capacity of &650&r complexity.

ftbuniversity.focuspouch.subtitle=制作一个 Focus Pouch
ftbuniversity.focuspouch.desc=The &bFocus Pouch&r has room for 18 Spell Foci, and can be worn as a Bauble.

ftbuniversity.rechargeped.subtitle=制作一个 Recharge Pedestal
ftbuniversity.rechargeped.desc1=Certain items require Vis to work, but lack the ability to use atmospheric Vis directly.
ftbuniversity.rechargeped.desc2=These items must be charged in the &bRecharge Pedestal&r.

ftbuniversity.workbenchcharger.subtitle=制作一个 Workbench Charger
ftbuniversity.workbenchcharger.desc=The &bWorkbench Charger&r is placed on top of the Arcane Workbench or Focal Manipulator, allowing them to &6use Vis from adjacent chunks&r instead of only the one it's in.

ftbuniversity.amuletofvis.subtitle=制作一个 Amulet of Vis
ftbuniversity.amuletofvis.desc=The &bAmulet of Vis&r, when charged and then worn, will &6charge items in your hotbar, baubles, or armor slots&r.

ftbuniversity.visbattery.title=Saving For a Rainy Day
ftbuniversity.visbattery.subtitle=制作一个 Vis Battery
ftbuniversity.visbattery.desc1=&bVis Batteries&r can be placed in a chunk, and will &6absorb Vis if the chunk is near full&r.
ftbuniversity.visbattery.desc2=If the chunk goes below 75%%, the Vis Battery will &6empty itself to refill the chunk&r.
ftbuniversity.visbattery.desc3=Each stores a rather pitiful amount, so it would be ideal to &6place several&r in a chunk.

ftbuniversity.unlockinfusion.title=Infusion
ftbuniversity.unlockinfusion.subtitle=Unlock Infusion
ftbuniversity.unlockinfusion.desc1=&bInfusion&r is the third school of magic, and it deals with the creation of certain items by &6infusing them with Essentia&r.
ftbuniversity.unlockinfusion.desc2=To begin with, 制作一个y of a set of &bThaumaturge's armor&r, which gives a Vis discount when crafting or casting.
ftbuniversity.unlockinfusion.task=Thaumaturge's armor

ftbuniversity.infusionaltar.title=Infusion Altar
ftbuniversity.infusionaltar.subtitle=Construct an Infusion Altar
ftbuniversity.infusionaltar.desc1=The &bInfusion Altar&r is a multiblock structure, and is where all infusion crafting is done.
ftbuniversity.infusionaltar.desc2=&6See the Thaumonomicon for building instructions.&r Use Salis Mundus on the Infusion Matrix to finalize it.
ftbuniversity.infusionaltar.desc3=Around the Altar, place Arcane Pedestals in a symmetric pattern; some recipes need more ingredients, and thus, more Pedestals.
ftbuniversity.infusionaltar.desc4=Arcane Infusions run the chance of &6instability&r, which can cause &cawful side effects&r, disrupting the infusion.
ftbuniversity.infusionaltar.desc5=To minimize instability, make sure the Altar and surrounding Pedestals are &6symmetric&r. You can also place certain blocks (Candles, Skulls, other creepy magic stuff) in the area to further increase stability (though again, make sure it's &6symmetric above all else&r).
ftbuniversity.infusionaltar.desc6=Infusion recipes require &6Essentia&r, which must be supplied in Warded Jars. These must be nearby, though you can use &6Essentia Mirrors&r instead.

ftbuniversity.pavingstones.title=Magic Stones
ftbuniversity.pavingstones.subtitle=Make Paving Stones
ftbuniversity.pavingstones.desc1=&bPaving Stones of Travel&r allow you to walk faster on them.
ftbuniversity.pavingstones.desc2=&bBarrier Stones&r prevent hostile mobs (and Golems) from crossing over them, and can be disabled with redstone.

ftbuniversity.infusionstones.title=Infusion Stones
ftbuniversity.infusionstones.subtitle=Make Infusion Stones
ftbuniversity.infusionstones.desc1=&bInfusion Speed Stones&r can be placed under the pillars of an Infusion Altar to make them faster, but require more Essentia.
ftbuniversity.infusionstones.desc2=&bInfusion Cost Stones&r make them slower, but require less Essentia.
ftbuniversity.infusionstones.task=Infusion Stones

ftbuniversity.infusionstabilizer.subtitle=Make Stabilizers
ftbuniversity.infusionstabilizer.desc1=&bStabilizers&r can be connected to Arcane Pedestals via &bRedstone Inlays&r to &6protect them from instability&r.
ftbuniversity.infusionstabilizer.desc2=In the event that an instability effect is about to happen to a protected Pedestal, it will instead go to the nearest connected Stabilizer and affect &nit&r instead. This will create &6atmospheric Flux&r.
ftbuniversity.infusionstabilizer.desc3=Stabilizers have a cooldown, so it may be smart to use &6multiple per Pedestal&r.

ftbuniversity.travellerboot.title=Made for Travelling
ftbuniversity.travellerboot.subtitle=Make Boots of the Traveller
ftbuniversity.travellerboot.desc1=&bBoots of the Traveller&r increase your &6walk and swim speed&r, allow you to &6jump higher&r and &6walk up blocks&r, and &6decreases fall damage&r.
ftbuniversity.travellerboot.desc2=They must be charged with Vis to function.

ftbuniversity.thaumarmor.title=Thaurmor
ftbuniversity.thaumarmor.subtitle=Make Thaumium Fortress armor
ftbuniversity.thaumarmor.desc1=&bThaumium Fortress armor&r is as protective as Diamond, and has much &6higher enchantability&r.
ftbuniversity.thaumarmor.desc2=The more pieces you have equipped, the more protective each is.
ftbuniversity.thaumarmor.task=Thaumium Fortress armors

ftbuniversity.elementaltools.title=And This is Why Tinkers' Isn't In
ftbuniversity.elementaltools.subtitle=制作一个y elemental tool
ftbuniversity.elementaltools.desc1=&bElemental tools&r have special effects that set them apart from normal, mundane tools. Sneaking will disable their extra powers.
ftbuniversity.elementaltools.desc2=The &bAxe of the Stream&r will break the &6farthest log first&r, so you can mine the whole tree by focusing on the same block. Holding right-click will &6pull items towards you&r.
ftbuniversity.elementaltools.desc3=The &bPickaxe of the Core&r has a chance of dropping &6Clusters&r, which smelt into two ingots. Right-clicking will &6show nearby ores&r.
ftbuniversity.elementaltools.desc4=The &bSword of the Zephyr&r has a chance to &6arc electricity&r to nearby mobs when used. When blocking, it will &6push entities away&r and &6block arrows&r, &6lifting you into the air&.
ftbuniversity.elementaltools.desc5=The &bShovel of the Earthmover&r digs a &63x3 area&r. Right-clicking will try to &6place a 3x3 square&r of that block, if you have enough.
ftbuniversity.elementaltools.desc6=The &bHoe of Growth&r will till a &63x3 area&r, and can also be &6used to fertalize&r crops.
ftbuniversity.elementaltools.task=Elemental tools

ftbuniversity.runicshielding.title=Runic Shielding
ftbuniversity.runicshielding.subtitle=Learn about Runic Shielding
ftbuniversity.runicshielding.desc1=&bRunic Shielding&r can be applied to any armor or bauble. For each level of Shielding, it &6adds half a heart of temporary health&r. This generates over time.
ftbuniversity.runicshielding.desc2=Though the Thaumonomicon only shows up to Runic Shielding +3, there's theoretically &6no limit to how high it can go&r.

ftbuniversity.cloudstepper.title=Skywalker
ftbuniversity.cloudstepper.subtitle=制作一个 Cloudstepper Ring
ftbuniversity.cloudstepper.desc=The &bCloudstepper Ring&r uses Vis to greatly &6reduce fall damage&r and give you a &6double jump&r.

ftbuniversity.headbandcuriosity.title=Thinking Cap
ftbuniversity.headbandcuriosity.subtitle=制作一个 Headband of Curiosity
ftbuniversity.headbandcuriosity.desc=The &bHeadband of Curiosity&r will generate &6knowledge from experience&r.

ftbuniversity.charmundying.title=The Undying
ftbuniversity.charmundying.subtitle=制作一个 Charm of Undying
ftbuniversity.charmundying.desc1=The &bCharm of Undying&r works exactly as a Totem of Undying, but works from the Bauble slots rather than your hand.
ftbuniversity.charmundying.desc2=Due to the relative annoyance of getting a Totem of Undying, &6this quest is optional&r.

ftbuniversity.verdantcharm.title=Contingency
ftbuniversity.verdantcharm.subtitle=制作一个 Verdant Heart Charm
ftbuniversity.verdantcharm.desc1=There are two &bVerdant Heart Charms&r, which use Vis to provide certain benefits.
ftbuniversity.verdantcharm.desc2=&bLifegiver&r will regenerate hearts, while &bSustainer&r will feed you and give you air.
ftbuniversity.verdantcharm.task=Verdant Heart Charms

ftbuniversity.unlockartifice.title=Artifice
ftbuniversity.unlockartifice.subtitle=Unlock Artifice
ftbuniversity.unlockartifice.desc1=&bArtifice&r is the school of magic dedicated to &6magical devices&r.
ftbuniversity.unlockartifice.desc2=The &bGoggles of Revealing&r, when worn, allow you to see certain things you couldn't otherwise, such as the Essentia in a Crucible, or the Essentia required by an Infusion Matrix.
ftbuniversity.unlockartifice.desc3=Many devices require Vis to work, which means you need the &6Recharge Pedestal&r in Auramancy.

ftbuniversity.arcanegrapple.title=GRAPPLING HOOK!
ftbuniversity.arcanegrapple.subtitle=制作一个 Arcane Grappler
ftbuniversity.arcanegrapple.desc1=The &bArcane Grappler&r will shoot an arcing projectile, then stick to whatever block it touches, pulling you through the air towards it.
ftbuniversity.arcanegrapple.desc2=While it isn't necessarily the most &ouseful&r form of transportation, it's &6super fun&r.

ftbuniversity.dioptra.subtitle=制作一个 Thaumic Dioptra
ftbuniversity.dioptra.desc1=The &bThaumic Dioptra&r, aside from being hard to spell, &6shows the Vis in a 13x13 chunk area&r, centered on itself.
ftbuniversity.dioptra.desc2=You can click it to toggle to showing those chunks' &6Flux&r instead.

ftbuniversity.infernalfurnace.title=Infurnal Fernace
ftbuniversity.infernalfurnace.subtitle=制作一个 Infernal Furnace
ftbuniversity.infernalfurnace.desc1=The &bInfernal Furnace&r is a multiblock furnace.
ftbuniversity.infernalfurnace.desc2=Items thrown in the top will slowly, but &6freely&r, be smelted and spit out the front.
ftbuniversity.infernalfurnace.desc3=Ores have a chance of creating additional Nuggets and Rare Earth, among other things.
ftbuniversity.infernalfurnace.desc4=Additionally, raw foods will smelt into Nuggets as well!
ftbuniversity.infernalfurnace.task=Look at an Infernal Furnace

ftbuniversity.bellows.title=Full of Hot Air
ftbuniversity.bellows.subtitle=制作一个rcane Bellows
ftbuniversity.bellows.desc1=&bArcane Bellows&r can be placed on the side of certain blocks to &6make them work faster&r.
ftbuniversity.bellows.desc2=These blocks include the &6Furnace&r, &6Infernal Furnace&r, &6Crucible&r, and &6Essentia Smelter&r.

# 👄
ftbuniversity.hungrychest.title=Voracious Vessel
ftbuniversity.hungrychest.subtitle=制作一个 Hungry Chest
ftbuniversity.hungrychest.desc=The &bHungry Chest&r will pick up any item that touches it, from any side. This is very useful for anything that drops items into the world, like &6mob farms&r or the &6Infernal Furnace&r.

ftbuniversity.arcanelevitator.title=You Lift Me Up
ftbuniversity.arcanelevitator.subtitle=制作一个 Arcane Levitator
ftbuniversity.arcanelevitator.desc1=The &bArcane Levitator&r will &6lift entities 8 blocks&r above itself, and sneaking allows them to descend.
ftbuniversity.arcanelevitator.desc2=When working, it uses up &61 Vis per second&r.
ftbuniversity.arcanelevitator.desc3=The bottom can be clicked to &6change the max distance&r, also changing the cost.
ftbuniversity.arcanelevitator.desc4=If placed &6horizontally&r, it will keep entities in the air while pushing them away.

ftbuniversity.redstonerelay.title=This is Definitely Magic, Yep, Totally
ftbuniversity.redstonerelay.subtitle=制作一个 Redstone Relay
ftbuniversity.redstonerelay.desc1=The &bRedstone Relay&r has two dials you can click, one sets the input strength and one sets the output strength.
ftbuniversity.redstonerelay.desc2=If the Relay receives an input that matches or exceeds the set input strength, it will output at the set output strength.

ftbuniversity.visgen.title=Wait, That's Illegal
ftbuniversity.visgen.subtitle=制作一个 Vis Generator
ftbuniversity.visgen.desc1=The &bVis Generator&r drains Vis from the chunk, converting it to &61,000 RF per Vis&r, though it can only output at 20RF/t.
ftbuniversity.visgen.desc2=A redstone signal will disable it.

ftbuniversity.arcaneear.title=Wizard Ears
ftbuniversity.arcaneear.subtitle=制作一个 Arcane Ear
ftbuniversity.arcaneear.desc1=The &bArcane Ear&r gives off a redstone pulse when it hears a &6Noteblock note&r that matches the one it's set to.
ftbuniversity.arcaneear.desc2=To set the Ear, treat it like a Noteblock. Place it on specific blocks for different instruments, and right-click to set the note.
ftbuniversity.arcaneear.desc3=There's a second form that toggles a signal when it hears the note, instead of pulsing.
ftbuniversity.arcaneear.task=Arcane Ear

ftbuniversity.autocross.title=Pew Pew
ftbuniversity.autocross.subtitle=制作一个 Automated Crossbow
ftbuniversity.autocross.desc1=The &bAutomated Crossbow&r will &6shoot at hostile mobs&r within 24 blocks of itself, assuming it can see them.
ftbuniversity.autocross.desc2=They exist as an entity, and have 30 health. Since they are an entity, then can &6ride Minecarts&r!
ftbuniversity.autocross.desc3=They &6need a supply of Arrows&r to shoot, which can be inserted manually or with Dispensers.

ftbuniversity.advancedcross.title=BRRRRRT
ftbuniversity.advancedcross.subtitle=制作一个 Advanced Automated Crossbow
ftbuniversity.advancedcross.desc1=The &bAdvanced Automated Crossbow&r fires faster, has more health, and allows you to &6configure what mobs it targets&r.
ftbuniversity.advancedcross.desc2=Other than that, it works exactly like the normal version.

ftbuniversity.arcanebore.title=Boring
ftbuniversity.arcanebore.subtitle=制作一个 Arcane Bore
ftbuniversity.arcanebore.desc1=The &bArcane Bore&r, when given a redstone signal and a pickaxe, will use atmospheric Vis to &6dig a large tunnel in front of it&r.
ftbuniversity.arcanebore.desc2=The pickaxe will take durability damage (though less than it would normally), but its enchantments will be applied to blocks broken.
ftbuniversity.arcanebore.desc3=The more enchantable the pickaxe, &6the larger area dug&r.
ftbuniversity.arcanebore.desc4=If there is an inventory adjacent to it, it will insert items there. Otherwise, items are dropped on the floor.
ftbuniversity.arcanebore.desc5=The Bore can &6ride Minecarts&r, which allows you to greatly increase the mined area!

ftbuniversity.arcanerail.title=Drive-by
ftbuniversity.arcanerail.subtitle=制作一个 Arcane Activator Rail
ftbuniversity.arcanerail.desc=Any Minecart containing a Crossbow or Bore that drives over the &bArcane Activator Rail&r will be toggled, turning on or off.

ftbuniversity.arcanelamp.title=I Love Lamp
ftbuniversity.arcanelamp.subtitle=制作一个 Arcane Lamp
ftbuniversity.arcanelamp.desc=The &bArcane Lamp&r will place additional light sources around itself, lighting up a larger area.

ftbuniversity.lampofblank.title=Mood Lighting
ftbuniversity.lampofblank.subtitle=Make the other magic Lamps
ftbuniversity.lampofblank.desc1=The &bLamp of Fertility&r uses &6Desiderium&r Essentia to convince mobs to breed. It only works when less than 8 of that mob are there.
ftbuniversity.lampofblank.desc2=The &bLamp of Growth&r uses &6Herba&r Essentia to fertilize nearby crops.

ftbuniversity.magicmirror.title=Mirror Mirror, On the Wall
ftbuniversity.magicmirror.subtitle=制作一个 Magic Mirror
ftbuniversity.magicmirror.desc1=When an item is thrown at a &bMagic Mirror&r, it will be sent to the Magic Mirror it is paired to. This allows you to &6teleport items&r across any distance.
ftbuniversity.magicmirror.desc2=To pair Mirrors, place one and then right-click it with another.
ftbuniversity.magicmirror.desc3=Mirrors can only be linked in pairs, you cannot have 2 inputs with 1 output.

ftbuniversity.handmirror.subtitle=制作一个 Magic Hand Mirror
ftbuniversity.handmirror.desc=The &bMagic Hand Mirror&r can be used to send items from your inventory to a linked Magic Mirror. 

ftbuniversity.essentiamirror.title=Essentia Teleportation
ftbuniversity.essentiamirror.subtitle=制作一个 Essentia Mirror
ftbuniversity.essentiamirror.desc1=The &bEssentia Mirror&r works like the Magic Mirror, but &6teleports Essentia&r instead.
ftbuniversity.essentiamirror.desc2=Essentia cannot be &6moved through with Tubes&r, they can only move through as clouds.
ftbuniversity.essentiamirror.desc3=That means you can only link from, say, Jars to the Infusion Matrix, or if you're using Essentia Transfusers.

ftbuniversity.golemancy.title=Golemancy
ftbuniversity.golemancy.subtitle=Unlock Golemancy
ftbuniversity.golemancy.desc1=&bGolemancy&r is the final main school of magic, which has to do with the creation of &6Golems&r.
ftbuniversity.golemancy.desc2=Golems are &6magical automatons&r that can be made to do certain actions, according to &6Control Seals&r.

ftbuniversity.brainjar.title=Think Tank
ftbuniversity.brainjar.subtitle=制作一个 Brain in a Jar
ftbuniversity.brainjar.desc=The &bBrain in a Jar&r will grab nearby experience and store it. Right-clicking it will &6collect the stored experience&r.

ftbuniversity.golempress.title=Mad Scientist's Workbench
ftbuniversity.golempress.subtitle=Construct a Golem Press
ftbuniversity.golempress.desc1=The &bGolem Press&r is a multiblock structure, and is where you &6create Golems&r.
ftbuniversity.golempress.desc2=See the Thaumonomicon for construction instructions.
ftbuniversity.golempress.desc3=At the top left, you can cycle through available &6Golem materials&r. Beneath, you can apply an &6addon module&r.
ftbuniversity.golempress.desc4=At the center-right, you can cycle through different &6body part options&r.
ftbuniversity.golempress.desc5=At the center, you can see the &6Golem's properties&r, and beneath you can see its &6stats&r, like its health.
ftbuniversity.golempress.desc6=On the far right, you can see the &6material and Essentia cost&r required to craft this Golem.
ftbuniversity.golempress.desc7=Quite honestly, the Thaumonomicon says everything that possibly could be said. Read that instead.
ftbuniversity.golempress.task=Look at a Golem Press

ftbuniversity.crimsonrites.title=Eldritch
ftbuniversity.crimsonrites.subtitle=Unlock Eldritch magic
ftbuniversity.crimsonrites.desc1=&bEldritch magic&r is the final school of magic, and is &6mostly unimplemented&r. However, there's still enough there that it's worth going over.
ftbuniversity.crimsonrites.desc2=To unlock the Eldritch tab, you have to &6scan a Crimson Cultist&r with the Thaumonomicon. After that, kill Cultists until one drops the &bCrimson Rites&r.
ftbuniversity.crimsonrites.desc3=Use the Crimson Rites (while you have plenty of Warp) and the Eldritch tab will unlock.

ftbuniversity.voidmetal.subtitle=Get Void Metal
ftbuniversity.voidmetal.desc1=&bVoid Metal&r is the final magic metal, crafted using &6Void Seeds&r.
ftbuniversity.voidmetal.desc2=Void Seeds drop from &6collapsing Flux Rifts&r, so it may be a good idea to &6purposefully create them&r by dumping tons of random stuff into a Crucible and allowing it to boil over.
ftbuniversity.voidmetal.desc3=Obviously, &cdo not do this at your base&r.

ftbuniversity.voidsiphon.subtitle=制作一个 Void Siphon
ftbuniversity.voidsiphon.desc=A &bVoid Siphon&r placed &6near a Void Rift&r will slowly drain the Rift, &6generating Void Seeds&r.

ftbuniversity.voidrobe.subtitle=Make Void Thaumaturge armor
ftbuniversity.voidrobe.desc1=&bVoid Thaumaturge armor&r has built-in Goggles of Revealing, repair themselves, high durability and armor, give Night Visions, and &6provide a higher Vis discount the more Warp you have&r.
ftbuniversity.voidrobe.desc2=Wearing this armor will slowly give you temporary Warp, which will evolve into Permanent Warp.
ftbuniversity.voidrobe.task=Void Thaumaturge Armor

ftbuniversity.primalcrusher.title=Yes, the Endgame Tool is a Paxel
ftbuniversity.primalcrusher.subtitle=制作一个 Void Crusher
ftbuniversity.primalcrusher.desc1=The &bVoid Crusher&r works as both a Pickaxe and a Shovel, and digs a 3x3 area.
ftbuniversity.primalcrusher.desc2=It also will &6slowly repair itself&r.

ftbuniversity.voidseer.subtitle=Make the Voidseer's Pearl
ftbuniversity.voidseer.desc=The &bVoidseer's Pearl&r is a bauble that gives you a Vis discount based on the amount of &6permanent Warp&r you have.

###Mahou Tsukai
ftbuniversity.mhchap.title=Mahou Tsukai

ftbuniversity.mhbook.title=The &oOther&r Blood Magic
ftbuniversity.mhbook.subtitle=Make the Mahou Tsukai Knowledge Compendium
ftbuniversity.mhbook.desc1=&eMahou Tsukai&r is a magic mod that, in short, is super fricken pretty. It claims to focus on "&6spell uniqueness and special effects&r."
ftbuniversity.mhbook.desc2=The &bMahou Tsukai Knowledge Compendium&r is the mod's guide book, and explains pretty much everything in detail.

ftbuniversity.bleeding.title=All That For a Drop of Blood
ftbuniversity.bleeding.subtitle=Take some damage
ftbuniversity.bleeding.desc1=Congratulations! You've &btaken damage&r, and now you have &6Bleeding&r! This is probably one of the first quests you'll complete, since you get Bleeding &oevery time you take damage&r.
ftbuniversity.bleeding.desc2=While you have the Bleeding effect (which you can also get with a &6Dagger&r), press &6M&r while aiming at the floor to draw a magic circle in blood. This will unlock your ability to access your mana, called &6Mahou&r.
ftbuniversity.bleeding.desc3=Mana is &6spent&r casting spells, and your &6max mana increases with use&r. Mana regenerates over time, &6based on how well fed you are&r. 
ftbuniversity.bleeding.desc4=Additionally, this Magic Circle is &6where spells are crafted&r.
ftbuniversity.bleeding.desc5=You can toggle the mana GUI with the command &6/showmahou&r.

ftbuniversity.attunedgem.subtitle=制作一个 Attuned gem
ftbuniversity.attunedgem.desc1=Right-clicking an &bAttuned gem&r will take some of your mana and &6store it&r in itself.
ftbuniversity.attunedgem.desc2=When casting spells, &6mana stored in a gem will be prioritized&r over your own mana.
ftbuniversity.attunedgem.desc3=Storing mana in a gem counts as using it, &6increasing your maximum mana&r.
ftbuniversity.attunedgem.task=Attuned Gems

ftbuniversity.powdered.title=Spell Components
ftbuniversity.powdered.subtitle=制作一个 Catalyst
ftbuniversity.powdered.desc1=&bCatalysts&r, like Powdered Iron and Quartz, are &6spell components&r. Each spell has a unique recipe of 3 Powders, which are to be used on a &6Blood Circle&r.
ftbuniversity.powdered.desc2=See the &6Mahou Tsukai Knowledge Compendium&r for a full list of spells, as well as their recipes. We've also gone through and added some information tabs in JEI.
ftbuniversity.powdered.desc3=Blood Circles are toggled by right-clicking them.
ftbuniversity.powdered.task=Catalysts

ftbuniversity.spellcloth.title=Scrolls
ftbuniversity.spellcloth.subtitle=制作一个 Spell Cloth
ftbuniversity.spellcloth.desc1=Certain spells can only be used as Scrolls, while some can only be used as Blood Circles.
ftbuniversity.spellcloth.desc2=To 制作一个 scroll, place down a &bSpell Cloth&r and &6draw a Blood Circle on it&r. Insert the spell components, then right-click the Spell Cloth to pick it up as a Scroll.
ftbuniversity.spellcloth.desc3=&6Only the scroll's creator can use it&r. Scrolls are used similarly to bows, and are &6one-use&r, though they stack up to 64.

ftbuniversity.faysight.title=Leylines
ftbuniversity.faysight.subtitle=制作一个 Scroll of the Mystic Eyes of Fey Sight
ftbuniversity.faysight.desc1=&6Leylines&r are paths that connect certain points throughout the world. Being near a Leyline or Leypoint &6increases your mana regeneration&r. Leylines also boost your &6Elytra speed&r.
ftbuniversity.faysight.desc2=The &6Fae&r are spiritlike creatures that spawn along Leylines, and are attracted to magic being cast. You can &6breed them&r with any Powdered Catalyst.
ftbuniversity.faysight.desc3=You can only see Leylines and the Fae using a &bScroll of the Mystic Eyes of Fey Sight&r, though they are still there when invisible. Each Scroll adds 30 seconds of &6Fay Sight&r effect; you can use multiple to increase it further.

ftbuniversity.fayessence.title=Fairy Dust
ftbuniversity.fayessence.subtitle=Get some Fae Essence
ftbuniversity.fayessence.desc1=&bFae Essence&r is dropped by the Fae, and can be used on the ground to place a &6Fae Circle&r.
ftbuniversity.fayessence.desc2=Fae Circles (which can also be made into Scrolls) work just look Blood Circles, but are ownerless. It is only &6bound to the person who most recently used it&r.
ftbuniversity.fayessence.desc3=As Fae Circle Scrolls are not bound to their creator, &6their creation can be automated&r.

ftbuniversity.mysticcode.title=Caster's Gauntlet
ftbuniversity.mysticcode.subtitle=制作一个 Mystic Code
ftbuniversity.mysticcode.desc1=The &bMystic Code&r can hold 3 stacks of Scrolls (open its GUI by sneak right-clicking).
ftbuniversity.mysticcode.desc2=Select a Scroll (by holding the Y button by default), then right click to use that Scroll.

ftbuniversity.firstsorcery.subtitle=制作一个 Mystic Code - First Sorcery
ftbuniversity.firstsorcery.desc1=The &bMystic Code - First Sorcery&r works like the Mystic Code, but &6does not delete Scrolls when they are used&r.
ftbuniversity.firstsorcery.desc2=However, as a trade off, it itself &6has durability&r.

ftbuniversity.manacircuit.subtitle=制作一个 Mana Circuit
ftbuniversity.manacircuit.desc1=&bMana Circuits&r are blocks that &6store mana&r, allowing it to be used by their owner if they are nearby.
ftbuniversity.manacircuit.desc2=Ownership is dictated by whoever right-clicks the Circuit first after it is placed.
ftbuniversity.manacircuit.desc3=Mana has to be &6manually given to the Circuit&r by right-clicking it, storing your own mana into it.
ftbuniversity.manacircuit.desc4=They only work when &6powered on&r, which is done by sneak right-clicking it.

ftbuniversity.bowweapon.title=Swords > Arrows
ftbuniversity.bowweapon.subtitle=Get a Bow of Weapon Projectiles
ftbuniversity.bowweapon.desc1=The &bBow of Weapon Projectiles&r will shoot weapons and tools in your inventory instead of Arrows.
ftbuniversity.bowweapon.desc2=You get it by using a &6Scroll of Weapon Projectiles&r.

ftbuniversity.ascension.title=Escape Rope
ftbuniversity.ascension.subtitle=制作一个 Ascension spell
ftbuniversity.ascension.desc1=&bAscension&r is a spell that has &6two forms&r, one as a Scroll and one as a Blood Circle.
ftbuniversity.ascension.desc2=As a &6Blood Circle&r, any entity (including items, mobs, and players) that stand on it will get teleported to the highest solid block directly above it automatically.
ftbuniversity.ascension.desc3=As a &6Scroll&r, it will teleport the caster to the highest block directly above them. This is very useful for when you're lost in caves.
ftbuniversity.ascension.desc4=This quest will automatically complete if either task is completed.
ftbuniversity.ascension.task=Look at an Ascension Blood Circle

ftbuniversity.treasury.title=Gate of Babylon
ftbuniversity.treasury.subtitle=Get a Treasury Projection Gauntlet
ftbuniversity.treasury.desc1=The &bTreasury Projection Gauntlet&r will summon portals that shoot weapons in your inventory (or Ender Chest and certain modded bags) at the block you are looking at.
ftbuniversity.treasury.desc2=These weapons are not actually removed from your inventory, nor can they be picked up.
ftbuniversity.treasury.desc3=You get it by using a &6Scroll of the Treasury Projection Gauntlet&r.

ftbuniversity.proxproj.title=Nothing Personnel, Kid
ftbuniversity.proxproj.subtitle=Get the Crimson Black Keys of Proximity Projection
ftbuniversity.proxproj.desc1=The &bCrimson Black Keys of Proximity Projection&r will allow you to &6teleport to a distant mob&r by aiming at it then attacking.
ftbuniversity.proxproj.desc2=You get it by using a &6Scroll of Proximity Projection&r.

ftbuniversity.megumin.title=Explosion!
ftbuniversity.megumin.subtitle=Get the Mystic Staff of Explosive Mana Condensation
ftbuniversity.megumin.desc1=The &bMystic Staff of Explosive Mana Condensation&r has 3 modes, which you can cycle through by sneak right-clicking.
ftbuniversity.megumin.desc2=In &6Big Explosion Mode&r, it has a very long chargeup time. Releasing will cause a massive explosion at the block you're aiming at, at the cost of &65000 mana&r.
ftbuniversity.megumin.desc3=In &6AOE Mode&r, it has a shorter chargeup time. Charging will summon portals behind you, aimed where you were aiming at the start, and releasing will send several explosive beams, at the cost of &6600 mana&r.
ftbuniversity.megumin.desc4=In &6Beam Mode&r, it has a short chargup time, but after which it will summon a massive destructive beam of magic in the direction you're aiming. This costs &6500 mana per tick&r.
ftbuniversity.megumin.desc5=You get it by using a &6Scroll of Explosive Mana Condensation&r.

ftbuniversity.spatdis.title=Yeet
ftbuniversity.spatdis.subtitle=Get the Mystic Staff of Spatial Disorientation
ftbuniversity.spatdis.desc1=The &bMystic Staff of Spatial Disorientation&r can be used on an entity (and held), then aimed in a direction and released to &6fling it in that direction&r. This costs &6200 mana&r.
ftbuniversity.spatdis.desc2=When used on a block, it will draw entities to it then launch them into the air. This costs &620 mana per second&r.
ftbuniversity.spatdis.desc3=You get it by using a &6Scroll of Spatial Disorientation&r.

ftbuniversity.caliburn.title=Dawnbreaker
ftbuniversity.caliburn.subtitle=Get Caliburn
ftbuniversity.caliburn.desc1=&bCaliburn&r is a magical sword that the undead fear, causing them to flee. Right-clicking will pull the undead and the caster towards each other.
ftbuniversity.caliburn.desc2=Get Caliburn using a Blood Circle of &6Power Consolidation&r, which creates a pool of Murky Water. &6Throw an enchanted sword into the pool&r (while you have &65000 mana&r) and it will be converted into Caliburn.
ftbuniversity.caliburn.desc3=Caliburn's damage depends on the sword thrown in, as well as its enchantments. The &6more damage it would deal to the undead&r (so, Smite and Sharpness), the &6more damage Caliburn will deal&r.
ftbuniversity.caliburn.desc4=You can enchant Caliburn and throw it into the pool to get an &6repeat the process&r, making it even more powerful.

ftbuniversity.contract.title=Blood Pact
ftbuniversity.contract.subtitle=制作一个 Contract blood circle
ftbuniversity.contract.desc1=Two players can place down &bContract&r blood circles near each other and stand on them to connect them.
ftbuniversity.contract.desc2=Players connected by Contracts will bypass certain effects from each other, such as Boundaries. To break a contract, one player must damage the other.
ftbuniversity.contract.task=Look at a Contract blood circle

ftbuniversity.durexch.title=Durability Exchange
ftbuniversity.durexch.subtitle=制作一个 Durability Exchange blood circle
ftbuniversity.durexch.desc1=The &bDurability Exchange&r blood circle will slowly &6use up the durability of items&r thrown on it (or in the inventory the blood circle is placed on), &6converting into mana&r.
ftbuniversity.durexch.desc2=If you can afford it, this is massively powerful since it can generate up to &650 mana per second&r, and stops working when you're full.
ftbuniversity.durexch.task=Look at a Durability Exchange blood circle

ftbuniversity.familiar1.title=Familiar, Why Is This So Familiar
ftbuniversity.familiar1.subtitle=制作一个 Scroll of Summon Familiar
ftbuniversity.familiar1.desc1=The &bScroll of Summon Familiar&r will spawn and bind a Familiar to you.
ftbuniversity.familiar1.desc2=Familiars will load the chunk they're in, and will let you know if it sees "interesting players, mobs, and blocks."

ftbuniversity.familiar2.title=Familiar Functions
ftbuniversity.familiar2.subtitle=制作一个y Scroll that requires a Familiar
ftbuniversity.familiar2.desc1=The &bScroll of Recall Familiar&r will teleport your Familiar to you.
ftbuniversity.familiar2.desc2=The &bScroll of Familiar Exchange&r will swap your Familiar's position with yours. You could use this then recall the Familiar to have an easy way to teleport back to your base from anywhere.
ftbuniversity.familiar2.desc3=The &bScroll of the Familiar's Garden&r will make the Familiar emit an aura of tranquility, preventing mobs from damaging each other.
ftbuniversity.familiar2.task=Familiar-related Scrolls

