ftbuniversity.ratchap.title=Rats

ftbuniversity.wildrat.title=Funny Rat Mod
ftbuniversity.wildrat.subtitle=Look at a Rat
ftbuniversity.wildrat.desc1=&eRats&r &bRats&r are a wild mobs that are generally a bit of a nuisance. However, they can be &6tamed and trained&r to do a variety of tasks.
ftbuniversity.wildrat.desc2=Wild Rats will try to &6eat&r whatever they can, including &6crops&r and even &6items in chests&r. They're also capable of &6bypassing Fences, Dirt, and Wood blocks&r, anything that logically wouldn't stop a rat.

ftbuniversity.plaguedoctor.title=I am a Doctor
ftbuniversity.plaguedoctor.subtitle=Look at a Plague Doctor
ftbuniversity.plaguedoctor.desc1=&bPlague Doctors&r are a special kind of Villager. They mostly trade in items related to death, poison, or Plague.
ftbuniversity.plaguedoctor.desc2=If they see anything sick with the Plague, be it a player or mob, they will throw &6Purifying Liquid&r at them, curing them.
ftbuniversity.plaguedoctor.desc3=If struck by lightning (or if a Plague Tome is used on them), the Plague Doctor will convert into the &6Black Death&r, a rather difficult boss monster.

ftbuniversity.plaguerat.subtitle=Look at a Plague Rat
ftbuniversity.plaguerat.desc1=&bPlague Rats&r are hostile mobs that &6carry Plague&r, infecting whatever they attack, including other Rats.
ftbuniversity.plaguerat.desc2=Plague is a potion effect that &6cannot be cured&r with Milk, and &6prevents health regen entirely&r.
ftbuniversity.plaguerat.desc3=Fortunately, &6tamed Rats are immune&r to the Plague.

ftbuniversity.cheese.title=Cheese, Please
ftbuniversity.cheese.subtitle=Get Cheese
ftbuniversity.cheese.desc1=&bBlocks of Cheese&r can be made by &6filling a Cauldron with Milk&r, and can be crafted into 4 &bCheese&r wedges.
ftbuniversity.cheese.desc2=You can &6throw Cheese at wild Rats&r to feed them, which has a chance of &6taming them&r.
ftbuniversity.cheese.task=Cheese

ftbuniversity.rattrap.title=OwO
ftbuniversity.rattrap.subtitle=制作一个 Rat Trap
ftbuniversity.rattrap.desc1=&bRat Traps&r can be placed on the ground and given &6Cheese as bait&r, which will attract wild Rats and &6kill them&r.
ftbuniversity.rattrap.desc2=Rats have a small chance of successfully eating the Cheese without getting killed.

ftbuniversity.tamerat.title=BFF
ftbuniversity.tamerat.subtitle=Tame a Rat
ftbuniversity.tamerat.desc1=Normally, Rats will try actively flee from players. However, Rats will gain &6trust&r with each Cheese they are fed, making them more friendly. Eventually, this can &btame the Rat&r.
ftbuniversity.tamerat.desc2=Tame Rats can be clicked to open the &6Rat menu&r, where you can give it a &6Helmet or Banner&r, a &6Rat Upgrade&r, and an &6item to hold&r.
ftbuniversity.tamerat.desc3=Most importantly, you can set a &6Command&r. There are 8 Commands you can cycle through, and each has an explanatory tooltip.
ftbuniversity.tamerat.desc4=Most most importantly, you can &6sneak right-click&r a tame Rat and it will &dride on your shoulder ❤&r 
ftbuniversity.tamerat.desc5=You can have up to 3 Rats riding you at once.

ftbuniversity.cheesestaff.subtitle=制作一个 Cheese Staff
ftbuniversity.cheesestaff.desc1=The &bCheese Staff&r can be used to &6bind Rats to blocks&r, setting their home, or allowing them to insert/extract items from that block.
ftbuniversity.cheesestaff.desc2=Right-click the Cheese Staff on the Rat, and then right-click again on the block/inventory you want to bind them to.

ftbuniversity.radiusstaff.subtitle=制作一个 Rat Radius Staff
ftbuniversity.radiusstaff.desc=Holding the &bRat Radius Staff&r will show the working area of Rats that have jobs.

ftbuniversity.plaguecure.title=My Cure Is Most Effective
ftbuniversity.plaguecure.subtitle=Get something to cure Plague
ftbuniversity.plaguecure.desc1=&bPurifying Liquid&r works as a splash potion effect, and &6cures the Plague&r. It can be &6bought from Plague Doctors&r, but they will attempt to cure you if you're sick for free anyway.
ftbuniversity.plaguecure.desc2=The items in the second task all also have a chance of curing Plague.
ftbuniversity.plaguecure.task=Home Remedies

ftbuniversity.ratups.title=Rat Upgrades
ftbuniversity.ratups.subtitle=制作一个 Rat Upgrade: Basic
ftbuniversity.ratups.desc1=Tamed Rats have a single slot to insert a &bRat Upgrade&r into.
ftbuniversity.ratups.desc2=Upgrades are really where the mod gets interesting. Upgrades can &6boost stats&r like health and speed, but they can also &6grant new abilities&r, like flight, or the ability to cook food.
ftbuniversity.ratups.desc3=Certain Rat Upgrades also work while the Rat is riding your shoulder!

ftbuniversity.ratcraft.title=Rat Crafting
ftbuniversity.ratcraft.subtitle=制作一个 Rat Crafting setup
ftbuniversity.ratcraft.desc1=Place a &bRat Crafting Table&r and place the desired item in the top left slot. If there are multiple recipes, cycle through them using the arrow buttons.
ftbuniversity.ratcraft.desc2=Insert the ingredients into the &6Input&r slots (with &6any form of automation&r (obviously Rats though, are you kidding?)).
ftbuniversity.ratcraft.desc3=Make sure a Rat with the &bRat Upgrade: Crafting&r is &6sitting on top of the Table&r (which may take a bit of finagling), and it will slowly craft that recipe.
ftbuniversity.ratcraft.desc4=The crafted items can be &6automatically removed&r by pipes, Hoppers, etc, but again, obviously use Rats. That's the whole point.

ftbuniversity.juryrig.subtitle=制作一个 Rat Upgrade: Jury-Rigged
ftbuniversity.juryrig.desc1=Right-clicking a &bRat Upgrade: Jury-Rigged&r opens its menu, allowing you to &6insert two other Rat Upgrades&r.
ftbuniversity.juryrig.desc2=You can give the filled Upgrade to a Rat, and it will &6use both Upgrades&r.
ftbuniversity.juryrig.desc3=You &6cannot separate Upgrades&r after combining them, nor can you &6combine combined upgrades&r.

ftbuniversity.ratuptips=See their tooltip for specific details on each.

ftbuniversity.ratitems.title=Item Transfer
ftbuniversity.ratitems.subtitle=制作一个 item-related Rat Upgrade
ftbuniversity.ratitems.desc=These Rat Upgrades make &6moving items&r more convenient.
ftbuniversity.ratitems.task=Item Rat Upgrades

ftbuniversity.ratenergy.title=Energy Transfer
ftbuniversity.ratenergy.subtitle=制作一个 Energy Transfer Rat Upgrade
ftbuniversity.ratenergy.desc1=These Rat Upgrades allow Rats to &6move RF&r instead of items.
ftbuniversity.ratenergy.desc2=The Cheese Staff will still say "Deposit/Take items," but it will move RF instead.
ftbuniversity.ratenergy.desc3=There are 4 tiers. The lowest tier moves &6100,000 RF&r, and the highest moves &6100,000,000 RF&r. It extracts/deposits instantly, but carrying it is &6only as fast as the Rat itself is&r.
ftbuniversity.ratenergy.task=Energy Transfer Rat Upgrades

ftbuniversity.ratfluid.title=Fluid Transfer
ftbuniversity.ratfluid.subtitle=制作一个 Bucket Rat Upgrade
ftbuniversity.ratfluid.desc1=These Rat Upgrades allow Rats to &6move Fluids&r instead of items.
ftbuniversity.ratfluid.desc2=The Cheese Staff will still say "Deposit/Take items," but it will move fluids instead.
ftbuniversity.ratfluid.desc3=There are 2 tiers, the first holding &61000mB&r and the second holding &65000mB&r. It extracts/deposits instantly, but carrying it is &6only as fast as the Rat itself is&r.
ftbuniversity.ratfluid.task=Bucket Rat Upgrades

ftbuniversity.ratcombat.title=Combat Upgrades
ftbuniversity.ratcombat.subtitle=制作一个 combat Rat Upgrade
ftbuniversity.ratcombat.desc=These Rat Upgrades give certain buffs or abilities that make them &6more effective in combat&r in some way.

ftbuniversity.ratharvest.title=Harvest Upgrades
ftbuniversity.ratharvest.subtitle=制作一个 harvest Rat Upgrade
ftbuniversity.ratharvest.desc=These Rat Upgrades give special abilities &6related to harvesting&r.

ftbuniversity.ratmovement.title=Movement Upgrades
ftbuniversity.ratmovement.subtitle=制作一个 movement Rat Upgrade
ftbuniversity.ratmovement.desc=These Rat Upgrades give Rats &6abilities related to movement&r.

ftbuniversity.ratspecial.title=Special Upgrades
ftbuniversity.ratspecial.subtitle=制作一个 special Rat Upgrade
ftbuniversity.ratspecial.desc=These Rat Upgrades are unique, and don't fit into a particular category.

ftbuniversity.ratfoods.title=Haha Yes, References
ftbuniversity.ratfoods.subtitle=Make Confit Byaldi and Potato Knishes
ftbuniversity.ratfoods.desc1=&bConfit Byaldi&r is a reference to the movie &6Ratatouille&r.
ftbuniversity.ratfoods.desc2=&bPotato Knishes&r are a reference to the wonderful video &6Potato Knishes&r by &6ratboygenius&r.

ftbuniversity.ratcage.title=Tiny Home
ftbuniversity.ratcage.subtitle=制作一个 Rat Cage
ftbuniversity.ratcage.desc1=&bRat Cages&r can be formed as a multiblock, and are used to &6contain and breed Rats&r.
ftbuniversity.ratcage.desc2=While a Rat is riding your shoulder, right-click the Rat Cage to insert it.
ftbuniversity.ratcage.desc3=When two Rats of opposite sex are in a Cage that has a &6Rat Breeding Lantern&r, they will breed, producing "Pinkies." Give them a couple days and they will grow into Rats.
ftbuniversity.ratcage.rewards=Rat Cage Decorations

ftbuniversity.ratlantis.title=This Dimension... Exists
ftbuniversity.ratlantis.subtitle=Learn about Ratlantis
ftbuniversity.ratlantis.desc1=&bRatlantis&r is a dimension that is home to several unique mobs and structures, and is normally &6integral to the progression of the mod&r.
ftbuniversity.ratlantis.desc2=However, the dimension... isn't exactly very good. Thankfully, the mod comes with a config option to &6disable it&r, which we've turned on.
ftbuniversity.ratlantis.desc3=Normally, the &bChunky Cheese Token&r spawns a portal to Ratlantis, but now it is simply a crafting component.
ftbuniversity.ratlantis.desc4=The Chunky Cheese Token is a very rare drop, so you may want to 制作一个 mob farm using &6Garbage Piles&r.

ftbuniversity.ratarch.subtitle=制作一个 Rat Upgrade: Archeologist
ftbuniversity.ratarch.desc1=The &bRat Upgrade: Archeologist&r allows you to &6make most Ratlantis items&r from normal Overworld items.
ftbuniversity.ratarch.desc2=With Ratlantis disabled, this is the only way to get Ratlantean items.
ftbuniversity.ratarch.desc3=See its uses in JEI with the U button to see what recipes are available.

ftbuniversity.feralrat.subtitle=Spawn a Feral Ratlantean
ftbuniversity.feralrat.desc1=As we've disabled Ratlantis, we've added in crafting recipes for the various Ratlantis-specific mobs.
ftbuniversity.feralrat.desc2=The &bFeral Ratlantean&r is a hostile mob with &640 hearts&r, and &6attacks anything not native to Ratlantis&r.
ftbuniversity.feralrat.desc3=It drops &6Feral Rat Claws&r, &6Rat Togas&r, and &6Rat Pelts&r. It also has a very rare chance of dropping a &6Ratlantean Automaton Head&r.

ftbuniversity.neorat.title=Nerd Rat
ftbuniversity.neorat.subtitle=Get a Vial of Consciousness
ftbuniversity.neorat.desc1=The &bVial of Consciousness&r can be &6thrown at a Feral Rat&r to transform it into the &6Neo-Ratlantean&r, a boss mob.
ftbuniversity.neorat.desc2=The Neo-Ratlantean has &6150 hearts&r and &6attacks everything not native to Ratlantis&r, including other monsters.
ftbuniversity.neorat.desc3=It very quickly flies around, opening portals that shoot projectiles. These projectiles can give various nasty effects, including spawning lightning.
ftbuniversity.neorat.desc4=It drops the &6Psionic Rat Brain&r, and is normally its only source.

ftbuniversity.ratflame.subtitle=Spawn a Ratlantean Spirit
ftbuniversity.ratflame.desc1=As we've disabled Ratlantis, we've added in crafting recipes for the various Ratlantis-specific mobs.
ftbuniversity.ratflame.desc2=The &bRatlantean Spirit&r is a hostile mob with &610 hearts&r, and &6attacks players and Villagers&r. They fly fairly quickly, and can &6phase through blocks&r. They deal damage by &6shooting Spirit Flame projectiles&r. 
ftbuniversity.ratflame.desc3=It drops &6Ratlantean Spirit Flames&r.

ftbuniversity.pirat.subtitle=Spawn a Pirat
ftbuniversity.pirat.desc1=As we've disabled Ratlantis, we've added in crafting recipes for the various Ratlantis-specific mobs.
ftbuniversity.pirat.desc2=The &bPirat&r is a hostile mob with two healthbars: the Pirat itself has &615 hearts&r and its boat has &630 hearts&r. If the Pirat dies first, the boat goes with it. If the Boat dies first, the Pirat stays but only attacks if walked into.
ftbuniversity.pirat.desc3=It sometimes drops a &6Pirat Hat&r.

ftbuniversity.rataut.title=Rat Golem
ftbuniversity.rataut.subtitle=Build and defeat the Ratlantean Automaton
ftbuniversity.rataut.desc1=The &bRatlantean Automaton&r is a boss mob that is summoned similarly to an Iron Golem, with the Core in the center and the Head on top.
ftbuniversity.rataut.desc2=It has &6300 hearts&r and has two attacks, one close and one ranged. It &6attacks all non-Ratlantean mobs&r, and is capable of &6breaking blocks&r softer than Obsidian.
ftbuniversity.rataut.desc3=It drops &6Arcane Technology&r and an &6Ancient Sawblade&r.

ftbuniversity.ratcombine.title=Moar Upgrades
ftbuniversity.ratcombine.subtitle=制作一个 Rat Upgrade Combiner
ftbuniversity.ratcombine.desc1=The &bRat Upgrade Combiner&r, as the name implies, allows you to &6combine Rat Upgrades&r. Unlike the Rat Upgrade: Jury-Rigged, there is &6no limit to how many Rat Upgrades can be combined&r (though you can still only have &6one of each&r).
ftbuniversity.ratcombine.desc2=Insert a &bRat Upgrade: Combined&r into the left slot, insert &bGems of Atlantis&r into the bottom slot for fuel, and then insert the &6Upgrade you wish to combine&r in the right slot.
ftbuniversity.ratcombine.desc3=The merged Rat Upgrade: Combined can be given to a Rat, and it will get the changes given by all of them.
ftbuniversity.ratcombine.desc4=You can throw a merged Rat Upgrade: Combined onto the &bRat Upgrade Separator&r, which will give you back all the Upgrades merged into it, as well as some of the Gems of Ratlantis.

ftbuniversity.ratlantisups.title=Ratlantean Upgrades
ftbuniversity.ratlantisups.subtitle=制作一个 Ratlantean Upgrade
ftbuniversity.ratlantisups.desc1=&bRatlantean Upgrades&r are &6significantly more powerful&r than normal ones, but are also generally more expensive.
ftbuniversity.ratlantisups.desc2=As always, see their tooltips for information on each specific one.

###Genetics Reborn
ftbuniversity.geneticschap.title=Genetics Reborn

ftbuniversity.scraper.title=Genetic Modification
ftbuniversity.scraper.subtitle=制作一个 Metal Scraper
ftbuniversity.scraper.desc1=&eGenetics Reborn&r is the spiritual successor to the classic mod &eAdvanced Genetics&r. It adds the ability to &6take genes from mobs and apply them to yourself&r.
ftbuniversity.scraper.desc2=The first step would be to 制作一个 &bMetal Scraper&r. Use it on a mob to get &6Organic Matter&r of that mob.

ftbuniversity.syringe.title=You'll Feel a Small Pinch
ftbuniversity.syringe.subtitle=制作一个 Glass Syringe
ftbuniversity.syringe.desc1=The &bGlass Syringe&r is used to get blood from yourself.
ftbuniversity.syringe.desc2=Freshly taken blood is &6contaminated&r, and must be processed before it can be used.

ftbuniversity.cellan.title=Cells at Work
ftbuniversity.cellan.subtitle=制作一个 Cell Analyser
ftbuniversity.cellan.desc=The &bCell Analyser&r converts Organic Matter into &6Cells&r of the same mob.

ftbuniversity.genoverclock.subtitle=制作一个 Overclocker
ftbuniversity.genoverclock.desc=&bOverclockers&r can be installed onto Genetics Reborn machines by right-clicking them.

ftbuniversity.gendna.subtitle=制作一个 DNA Extractor
ftbuniversity.gendna.desc=The &bDNA Extractor&r converts Cells into &6DNA Helixes&r of the same mob.

ftbuniversity.dnadecrypt.subtitle=制作一个 DNA Decryptor
ftbuniversity.dnadecrypt.desc1=The &bDNA Decryptor&r will take a DNA Helix and decrypt it, finding its &6Gene type&r.
ftbuniversity.dnadecrypt.desc2=Gene types are essentially what "power" the gene gives. For instance, Milky gives the ability to be milked.

ftbuniversity.plasmid.title=Vigors
ftbuniversity.plasmid.subtitle=制作一个 Plasmid Infuser
ftbuniversity.plasmid.desc1=&bPlasmids&r can have gene types infused into them in the &bPlasmid Infuser&r.
ftbuniversity.plasmid.desc2=Place the Plasmid in the right slot, and the DNA Helixes in the left. The &6gene type of the first Helix&r (which can't be basic) is what chooses what gets infused into the Plasmid.
ftbuniversity.plasmid.desc3=You need to provide it with 24 "points". A &6basic gene&r is worth 1 point, and a &6gene of the same type&r as the first is worth 2 points.

ftbuniversity.bloodpure.subtitle=制作一个 Blood Purifier
ftbuniversity.bloodpure.desc=The &bBlood Purifier&r takes a contaminated Syringe and purifies it, allowing it to be worked with.

ftbuniversity.plasinjec.subtitle=制作一个 Plasmid Injector
ftbuniversity.plasinjec.desc1=The &bPlasmid Injector&r takes a completed Plasmid and a purified Syringe and combines them.
ftbuniversity.plasinjec.desc2=This will put the gene into the Syringe but also contaminate it again, so you will have to purify it again.

ftbuniversity.antiplasmid.title=Non-GMO
ftbuniversity.antiplasmid.subtitle=制作一个 Anti Plasmid
ftbuniversity.antiplasmid.desc=Craft an Anti Plasmid with a completed Plasmid to set the gene, then inject it like a Plasmid to &6remove that gene&r.

ftbuniversity.genelink.title=Click here for a list of genes
ftbuniversity.genelink.subtitle=This link goes to the mods' wiki page, with a list of all Genes and what mobs give them.

ftbuniversity.cloning.subtitle=制作一个 Cloning Machine
ftbuniversity.cloning.desc1=The &bCloning Machine&r uses a rather large amount of RF (50k, per mob) to spawn a mob.
ftbuniversity.cloning.desc2=Use an &bAdvanced Scraper&r on a mob, then put it into the left slot of the Cloning Machine, and it will start.

